        "version_name": "New King James Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Thus He showed me: Behold, the Lord stood on a wall made with a plumb line, with a plumb line in His hand."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Then he showed me another vision. I saw the Lord standing beside a wall that had been built using a plumb line. He was using a plumb line to see if it was still straight."
      }
